EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
STRAIT OF GIBRALTAR.
GIBRALTAR TO CANARY ISLANDS.
DNC 01, DNC 08.
1. TEN METER S/V MIA, WHITE HULL, ONE PERSON ON BOARD,
   OVERDUE DUE TO ENGINE FAILURE,
   GIBRALTAR (36-08N 005-27W)
   TO CANARY ISLANDS. LAST KNOWN POSITION IN
   34-11N 009-21W AT 192043Z JUN.
   VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP
   LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO MRCC RABAT,
   PHONE: 2125 3762 5877, 2125 3762 5897,
   FAX: 2125 3762 5017,
   E-MAIL: MRCC.RABAT@MPM.GOV.MA, MRCCRABAT@GMAIL.COM.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1987/18.
